---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------
Thorn Whip
---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------
NOTE: These formulas use global_attack_mod to store static modifiers.  
    -You must have at least one mod selected or the macro breaks.  Create a Placeholder with a value of 0 to make sure macros work. 
    -Placing a space after the damage will make the formula easier to view. For example, rage should look like "2 "

NOTE:These formulas use global_damage_mods to store additional dice.  
    -You don't have to keep any global dice mods checked.  Macros will work either way.
    -Placing a space after the damage will make the formula easier to view.  
    -To prevent red/green make sure to do a critical fail 1 less than dice minimum and critical success 1 higher than dice maximum.  For example, bless should look like what's in quotes "1d6cf<0cs>5 ".
---------------------------------------------


---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------
Thorn Whip
---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
Thorn Whip - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
ThornWhip-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
ThornWhip-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee Spell Attack - Thorn Whip&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} lashes out with a Thorn Whip*&#125;&#125; {{Range=30'&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[ [[1d6!cf<1cs>6+ [[1+floor((@{selected|level}+1)/6)-1]]d6cf<0cs>100]] [Spell Dice]]] [Spell Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Spell=$[[1]] Piercing&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[3]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[4]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Hit=If the attack hits, the target is pulled 10' closer to @{Selected|character_name} &#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
ThornWhip-Advantage-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee Spell Attack - Thorn Whip (Advantage)&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} lashes out with a Thorn Whip at **Advantage** *&#125;&#125; {{Range=30'&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[ [[2d6!!cf<1cs>10kh1 + [[1+floor((@{selected|level}+1)/6)-1]]d6cf<0cs>100]] [Spell Dice]]] [Spell Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Spell=$[[1]] Piercing&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[3]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[4]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Hit=If the attack hits, the target is pulled 10' closer to @{Selected|character_name} &#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
