Thorn Whip - Unnested Macros - Works on it's own, but not in a nested query
---------------------------------------------
ThornWhip-Standard
&{template:default} {{name=Melee Spell Attack - Thorn Whip}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} lashes out with a Thorn Whip*}} {{Range=30'}} [[ [[ [[ [[1d6!cf<1cs>6+ [[1+floor((@{selected|level}+1)/6)-1]]d6cf<0cs>100]] [Spell Dice]]] [Spell Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Spell=$[[1]] Piercing}} {{Dice Mods=$[[3]] Varies}} {{Static=$[[5]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[4]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage**  }} {{Hit=If the attack hits, the target is pulled 10' closer to @{Selected|character_name} }}
