---------------------------------------------
Thorn Whip with Piercer Feat - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
ThornWhip-Piercer-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Piercer-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Piercer-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Piercer-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Piercer-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Piercer-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Piercer-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|ThornWhip-Piercer-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
ThornWhip-Piercer-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee Spell Attack - Thorn Whip&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} lashes out with a Thorn Whip*&#125;&#125; {{Range=30'&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[ [[1d6!cf<1cs>6+ [[1+floor((@{selected|level}+1)/6)-1]]d6cf<0cs>100]] [Spell Dice]]] [Spell Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Spell=$[[1]] Piercing&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[3]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[4]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Hit=If the attack hits, the target is pulled 10' closer to @{Selected|character_name} &#125;&#125; {{Piercer Hit=Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals piercing damage, you can reroll one of the attack's damage dice, and you must use the new roll. &#125;&#125; {{Piercer Crit= On a critical - deal an additional [[1d6cf<0cs>100]] Piercing&#125;&#125;
